{"tid":4090,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"比人搶左個名 就好似比人搶左條女咁","createTime":"2016-11-26T11:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T01:54:00.000Z","uid":24524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40f0f3a3778caa1930945e90729aa2fe47f336fc","tid":4090,"uid":24524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:28:04.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打同我一樣 轉黎新台個陣比人快一步登記左以前係高登用開個名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然話呢個名唔係我獨有，人人都有權改名叫死獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但用開有感情，同埋獌區嘅巴打一睇都叫認得下個名，知道係小弟黎9up下啦⋯ 又好似大家見到韓費呀，俾盡呀，47歲（破產）咁多位巴打呀，咁有親切感咁。<br />\n唉，好似比人搶左條女咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌"},{"pid":"2b6fa025ad6cf24cefdadd2d7d7283e15ab6bc83","tid":4090,"uid":24524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>"},{"pid":"2eacc879bf9251878451371d4655e6b6179253f2","tid":4090,"uid":24524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:08:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>"},{"pid":"53703c61dbbba4c56f3eb1b3a7e3abeeffdd36b9","tid":4090,"uid":5039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:21:03.000Z","msg":"那有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6602449f4d7ee1d4a7168cbf2b6a2c667503116","tid":4090,"uid":24524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>那有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bd5c0b2f0c47e28958518ea77568a557391dc0","tid":4090,"uid":11310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":